snippet.title: [Kickstarter Trailer] Self-Checkout Unlimited
snippet.description:
Self-Checkout Unlimited is a surreal, philosophical adventure game set inside a nostalgic late 90s mall. 

NOW ON KICKSTARTER: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/argentgames/self-checkout-unlimited-a-3d-mall-adventure

PLAY THE DEMO: https://argent-games.itch.io/self-checkout-unlimited

Trailer featuring the VO of Katie Flamman (www.katieflamman.co.uk)
